---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/legal.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Delete your account — Attic"
  description="How to delete your Attic account and the data associated with it, or request deletion of specific data."
  ogTitle="Delete your account — Attic"
  ogDescription="Delete your Attic account and associated data, or request data deletion."
>

<header class="legal-hero"><div class="wrap">
<p class="eyebrow">Account</p>
<h1>Delete your account</h1>
<p>How to permanently delete your Attic account and the data tied to it.</p>
</div></header>

<section class="legal"><div class="wrap">
<div class="legal__body">

<h2 id="in-app">Delete your account in the app</h2>
<p>You can delete your account at any time from inside the Attic app:</p>
<ol>
<li>Open the Attic app and sign in.</li>
<li>Go to <strong>Profile → Delete account</strong>.</li>
<li>Type <strong>DELETE</strong> to confirm.</li>
</ol>
<p>Your account is closed immediately and you're signed out.</p>

<h2 id="crates">Before you delete: return any crates</h2>
<p>If you still have crates with us — at your home or in storage — we'll ask you to schedule their final pickup or return first. Once every crate is back with Attic, you can complete the deletion. The app walks you through this.</p>

<h2 id="what-happens">What gets deleted</h2>
<p>When you delete your account, we remove your saved personal information from the app, including your name, email address, phone number, and service address, and we delete your sign-in identity. Your subscription stops renewing.</p>
<p>For legal, accounting, and dispute-resolution reasons, we retain a limited record of past transactions (handled by our payment processor, Stripe) and a record that the account existed. We do not keep your contact details or address. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details on retention.</p>

<h2 id="partial">Request deletion of specific data</h2>
<p>If you'd like to request deletion of specific data without closing your account, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@attic.it.com">privacy@attic.it.com</a> and we'll handle your request.</p>

<h2 id="contact">Questions</h2>
<p>For anything about your data or this process, contact <a href="mailto:privacy@attic.it.com">privacy@attic.it.com</a>.</p>

</div>
</div></section>

</BaseLayout>
